About me

Hello everyone!

My name is Dmitry

I am a Full-Stack & Software Engineer with a special bias towards creativity and innovation. I am also involved in graphic design. My actions are always aimed at achieving high results and quality fulfillment of tasks. In life I am guided by self-development, I never stand still.

I maintain an active position in life, participate in hackathons.
I am a multiple winner of international hackathons, and on the state's registry of persons of outstanding ability.

Currently I develop open-source projects, as well as sometimes I work on freelancing. I develop websites, applications, bots, algorithms. I know how to work with big data. I am actively studying Rust for high-performance applications.
